OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering 25-
OL,4,Cyear-old man
OL,6,FA man has been sentenced to life
OL,7,Fimprisonment after being found guilty
OL,8,Fof murdering a 25-year-old man in
OL,9,FBristol last summer.
OL,11,FShakawan Siddiqi was sentenced at
OL,12,FBristol Crown Court on Friday 11th
OL,13,FJuly for the killing of Kunta Ceesay.
OL,15,FThe 32-year-old stabbed Mr Ceesay
OL,16,Fduring a street altercation on
OL,17,FStapleton Road on 20 September 2024.
OL,19,FMr Ceesay died from his injuries later
OL,20,Fthat day.
