OL,4,Cyear-old man
OL,6,FSiddiqi was convicted of murder in
OL,7,FApril 2025 following a two-and-a-half-
OL,8,Fweek trial and was remanded in custody
OL,9,Fpending sentencing.
OL,11,FThe court heard that it remains
OL,12,Funclear whether Mr Ceesay knew
OL,13,FSiddiqi, though there may have been a
OL,14,Fprevious dispute involving a small sum
OL,15,Fof money.
OL,17,FSiddiqi, from St Paul's, received a
OL,18,Flife sentence and must serve a minimum
OL,19,Fterm of 21 years and 74 days.
