OL,6,FThe sentence also covers unrelated
OL,7,Fconvictions for a wounding offence and
OL,8,Fpossession of a bladed article from
OL,9,FFebruary last year.
OL,11,FWhen Siddiqi was found guilty, Kunta's
OL,12,Ffamily released a statement saying:
OL,13,F"Kunta was a kind, bubbly, and loving
OL,14,Fboy who always helped his family and
OL,15,Ffriends whenever he could.
OL,17,F"Everyone liked him and they would
OL,18,Fconfide in him because of how open he
OL,19,Fwas.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
