OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murdering 25-
OL,4,Cyear-old man
OL,6,F"It is so sad for the family that
OL,7,FKunta was taken from us far too soon
OL,8,Fand he has been robbed of the chance
OL,9,Fto grow old, create his own family and
OL,10,Freach his dreams.
OL,12,F"It's difficult to comprehend the
OL,13,Fsenseless way that Kunta has lost his
OL,14,Flife and how difficult it will be for
OL,15,Fall of us to have to live without him.
OL,17,F"Whilst our hearts and lives will
OL,18,Fnever be the same, we the family of
OL,19,FKunta trusted the justice system and
OL,20,Fthe jurors to make the right decision
OL,21,Fin this case."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
