OL,6,FThey added "We are so grateful for the
OL,7,Fwork done by the police and
OL,8,Fprosecution in bringing Siddiqi to
OL,9,Fjustice.
OL,11,F"We are happy with the verdict and
OL,12,Falthough it won't bring Kunta back, it
OL,13,Fhas reinforced our faith in the
OL,14,Fjustice system and the police.
OL,16,F"Kunta's life meant something, and we
OL,17,Fhope that this will serve as a
OL,18,Freminder for people to be cautious,
OL,19,Flead with kindness and love in their
OL,20,Flives."
